    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "「――今年のバレンタインも、あなたと一緒に」……\nはぁぁ～……麻奈様は何度見ても麗しいですわ～",
      "startTime": 5.8666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5866.666666599999,
          "startTime": 11.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "すず、お疲れ様。ん？　それは……\n麻奈のバレンタインのCMか",
      "startTime": 17.7999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "その通りですわ！　毎年この時期になると\n決まってこのCMを観返したくなるんですの",
      "startTime": 24.466666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "俺も毎年、すずと同じように観返してるよ\n繰り返し観たくなるんだよな、麻奈のCMは",
      "startTime": 31.6333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですのよ！　一度ならず二度、いえ……\n何度でも観たくなるのが麻奈様の魅力ですわよね！",
      "startTime": 40.0704227667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "「私から君へのバレンタインチョコだよ\nもちろん本気の本気。本命チョコ」",
      "startTime": 48.566666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "「……照れないの。君は鈍いんだから\nこれくらいはっきり言わなきゃ伝わらないでしょ？」",
      "startTime": 56.6312394869,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}